item.description: -h, –help help for hugo –i18n-warnings print missing translations –ignoreCache ignores the cache directory –ignoreVendor ignores any _vendor directory -l, –layoutDir string filesystem path to layout directory –log enable Logging –logFile string log File path (if set, logging enabled automatically) –minify minify any supported output format (HTML, XML etc.) –noChmod don’t sync permission mode of files –noTimes don’t sync modification time of files –path-warnings print warnings on duplicate target paths etc.
